</Paragraph>

<Paragraph Style="{DynamicResource HeaderParagraphStyle}">Features:</Paragraph> 
<List>
<ListItem><Paragraph>	Supports text formatting, bulleted and numbered lists.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>	Formatting includes setting up of Font Name, Font Colour, Font Size, Font Styles (such as Italic, Underline and Bold), Alignment, Indent, Subscript and Superscript, Shadow, and Spacing.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>	Supports special formatting for a paragraph as well, including Keeping lines together, and Keeping with next, etc., </Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>
